<description>Lee had a mixed time for Hartlepool in the 2000-01 campaign. He began the season in fine style, scoring both goals in a great 2-0 win at Lincoln on the opening day but his form was subsequently a little patchy, and when Pool signed Mark Tinkler he was relegated to the subs' bench. He is a promising young midfield player who makes darting runs at opposition defences. Lee was surprisingly released in the summer. After a brief spell with Leigh RMI in the Conference, Lee joined Rossendale United.</description>

